1. *Pobegao* je od kuće nakon što je čuo krikove iz sobe. (He ran away from home after he heard screams from the room.)

2. Dok se *pobeglo* od nas, trčao je kroz šumu. (While running away from us, he was running through the forest.)

3. Njegova majka se nada da će se on *pobeti* i vratiti kući. (His mother hopes that he will escape and return home.)

4. Policija je tragala za njim kad je *pobegao*. (The police were searching for him when he escaped.)

5. On se *pobegne* od svojih bivših prijatelja. (He escapes from his former friends.)